# Fixture templates are structure-only (data values cleared by scripts/build_fixture_templates.py).
# Formulas preserved; safe to commit for CI tests on fresh checkout.
# docs/references/*.xlsx remain gitignored — they contain real Humax financial data.
!fixtures/templates/*.xlsx

